channel.title: H3lp pl0x
channel.description:
Alright, so, i enjoy playing on my regular hybridscape account (moparscape 3.2 w/ aryan), Not connected to the internet. :o I know, it's sort of strange, but i do. Now, i've heard of the new-ish silab items w/ skill capes and what not. Could someone please make a server, not connected with the internet, or server or what ever that is silab capible? If so, please mail me it, or just reply. I would also love it if someone would fix acouple bugs is 3.2 and add some other newer items. I was trying to do that, but failed. and also, i added fire cape and fury and what ever else, and they sort of work, but when i take them off and then put one back on, they turn into a tz(something or other) noted and are basically worthless. I also cannot bank these new items i added to the data cfg item file thing, or basically just open any other interface, w/o it corrupting into the other item. Please If you help i would ~(GREATLY)~ appriciate it!!!!! if not, well.... :mad: :mad: :mad: :mad: :mad: :mad: :P. well thank you for reading this. BYE
E-mail is nbaker61@columbus.rr.com.
